These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, sunflower, orchid, daffodil
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, lizard, turtle
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, may, april, july
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the owner of the cat##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the ferret is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who growssunflower##2
6. the person who's birthday is in may is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Flower        | orchid | daffodil  | sunflower | aconite  |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret  | cat       | lizard     |
| Birthday   | april     | december | july       | may |

