.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, magic-tricks, reading
House: ranch-style, victorian, palace, craftsman
City: nizza, san-francisco, marseilles, rome
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to rome is between the craftsman house and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the craftsman house is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
7. the palace house is the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | chess    | reading  | magic-tricks |
| House   | craftsman  | ranch-style  | victorian   | palace    |
| City         | san-francisco | rome | nizza | marseilles      |

