.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, dahlia, orchid, amaryllis
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, blueberry, apple, nectarine
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, folk, house, indie
1. the fan of folk is between the fan of indie and the person who growsdahlia##2
2. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the far right##1
5. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
6. the fan of country is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the fan of house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Flower      | dahlia | amaryllis         | marigold   | orchid    |
| Food         | blueberry | nectarine | eggplant | apple |
| Music-Genre   | house   | folk        | indie      | country   |

