.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, dutch, german, polish
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, board-games, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, salsa, jazz, dubstep
1. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
2. the fan of blues is between the fan of dubstep and the polish##2
3. the german is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the german is on the right of the australian##1
6. the fan of dubstep is between the person who's hobby is camping and the fan of salsa##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | polish        | dutch   | australian | german |
| Hobby         | board-games | camping | card-games    | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre     | jazz       | blues     | dubstep       | salsa    |

