.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, cranberry, cucumber, mango
City: hannover, marseilles, colone, prague
4 different pets are kept: horse, hedgehog, mouse, bird
1. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person eating cherry is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is between the person traveling to prague and the owner of the mouse##2
6. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating cherry and the person eating cucumber##2
7. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | cucumber | cranberry  | cherry | mango      |
| City   | colone  | prague  | hannover | marseilles |
| Pet   | bird | horse | hedgehog | mouse     |

