.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, doctor, nurse, journalist
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, baking, filmmaking, video-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, handball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the nurse is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the doctor is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
7. the journalist is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job          | nurse  | doctor    | journalist | analyst  |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | video-games       | baking        | skydiving    |
| Sport         | cycling | badminton | volleyball  | handball |

