.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, bridge, billiard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, hip-hop, r&b, gospel
4 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, lizard, rabbit
1. the fan of gospel is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is between the owner of the rabbit and the person playing snooker##2
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
6. the person playing bridge is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Game         | billiard  | snooker | bridge | chess |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | gospel | hip-hop   | r&b         |
| Pet           | hamster | lizard  | horse   | rabbit      |

