.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, mango, pepper, tomato
City: paris, hamburg, colone, boston
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, golf, parkour
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is the person eating eggplant##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person traveling to colone is the person eating mango##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
6. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
7. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person who's sport is golf and the person traveling to paris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | tomato  | eggplant    | pepper | mango       |
| City         | boston | hamburg | paris  | colone |
| Sport   | golf   | parkour      | handball  | climbing     |

