.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, orange, pepper, pomegranate
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, tiparillo, vegafina, bluemaster
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, project-manager, photographer, mechanic
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
3. the person eating orange is between the person eating lettuce and the tiparillo-smoker##2
4. the project-manager is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the project-manager is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the mechanic is the bluemaster-smoker##1
8. the paramedic is the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | pepper      | pomegranate | orange | lettuce |
| Cigar         | bluemaster   | tiparillo  | dannemann | vegafina |
| Job   | mechanic | paramedic   | project-manager | photographer |

