.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, march, november
City: new-york, edinburgh, boston, prague
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, guinea-pig, rat
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the owner of the dog is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person traveling to boston##2
4. the person traveling to boston is between the owner of the dog and the person who's birthday is in november##2
5. the person traveling to boston is the owner of the rat##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is the owner of the goat##1
7. the person traveling to prague is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday    | november  | march | august | april     |
| City   | new-york | boston   | prague  | edinburgh    |
| Pet     | goat        | rat       | dog      | guinea-pig |

