.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dressmaker, pilot, firefighter
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, sudoku, traveling
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, old-henry, tiparillo, chaman
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the firefighter##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the pilot##1
3. the dressmaker is between the pilot and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the dressmaker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
6. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Job   | firefighter | pilot     | dressmaker | bartender       |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | traveling | card-games  | gardening |
| Cigar        | chaman  | old-henry      | tiparillo        | dannemann      |

