.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, milk, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, september, may, july
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, volleyball, weightlifting, handball
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is between the person drinking milk and the person who's birthday is in april##2
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person drinking water is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | water  | milk       | fanta   |
| Birthday      | april     | may | september | july |
| Sport        | weightlifting        | handball | basketball     | volleyball |

