.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, rat, rabbit, hamster
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, romance, time-travel
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, video-games, hiking, collecting
1. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person watching romance movies and the owner of the rabbit##2
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Pet           | rat | hamster | rabbit    | cat   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance      | fantasy   | time-travel | disaster |
| Hobby     | chess     | video-games       | hiking        | collecting    |

