.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
House: cape-cod, colonial, modern, tower
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, oliveros, montecristo, bluemaster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour, rugby, sailing
1. the modern house is the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the tower house##1
3. the cape-cod house is the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the modern house is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the davidoff-smoker and the cape-cod house##2
6. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| House   | modern   | colonial           | cape-cod         | tower      |
| Cigar     | davidoff | montecristo | bluemaster | oliveros |
| Sport   | rugby     | parkour         | biathlon       | sailing        |

