.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, yellow, mauve, apricot
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, coach, social-worker, photographer
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indian, italian, mexican
1. the musician is the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person who likes blue is between the person who likes mauve and the indian##2
3. the person who likes mauve is the coach##1
4. the person who likes mauve is between the social-worker and the mexican##2
5. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
6. the german is between the italian and the photographer##2
7. the musician is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Color      | yellow | mauve | blue   | apricot |
| Job   | musician  | coach    | social-worker   | photographer     |
| Nationality   | mexican  | italian | german | indian   |

