.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, airplane, trike, roller
House: cape-cod, wooden, farmhouse, art-deco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, swimming, weightlifting
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
2. the farmhouse house is between the person driving the roller and the person who's sport is swimming##2
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
6. the wooden house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
7. the person driving the trike is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Transport   | helicopter    | airplane | roller           | trike |
| House       | cape-cod | farmhouse    | wooden          | art-deco   |
| Sport      | swimming  | rugby   | weightlifting | cricket  |

