.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, trike, tram
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon, climbing, ice-hockey
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, horse, mouse
1. the person who's sport is climbing is the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's sport is swimming##2
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the person driving the skateboard and the owner of the cat##2
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Transport      | trike | motorbike | skateboard     | tram   |
| Sport   | swimming | ice-hockey        | climbing  | biathlon  |
| Pet           | cat      | mouse         | hedgehog | horse |

