3. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person who likes green##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the owner of the snake is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the owner of the goldfish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Color         | ebony        | green  | blue | grey   |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | surfing    | snowboarding |
| Pet   | fish        | goldfish     | snake       | rabbit      |

