.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, brown, white, chestnut
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, hamster, hedgehog
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold, sunflower, azalea
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person who likes white is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsazalea is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the cat is between the person who likes chestnut and the person who growssunflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Color        | chestnut | brown | blood-red | white |
| Pet         | bird       | cat     | hamster   | hedgehog   |
| Flower   | bellflower | marigold | sunflower | azalea |

 